{"tid":2223594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登：川普是俄羅斯總統的走狗","createTime":"2020-09-30T03:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T03:57:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"912c7dcd19d451ef642fa143c44aa7e510676f77","tid":2223594,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"民主黨籍總統候選人拜登今天在2020年美國總統大選首場辯論會指控共和黨籍總統川普，是俄羅斯總統蒲亭（Vladimir Putin）的走狗。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，拜登今天在俄亥俄州克里夫蘭（Cleveland）凱斯西儲大學（Case Western Reserve University）舉行的辯論中，稱自己擔任前總統歐巴馬副手期間，「與蒲亭正面交鋒，清楚跟他說，你拿不走我們的東西」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登旋即指控川普，說川普「是蒲亭的走狗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%98%AF%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B0%E7%8B%97-024522799.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB-%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%258B%2597-024522799.html&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=d90aac22\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%98%AF%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B0%E7%8B%97-024522799.html</a>"},{"pid":"524e6bf91ff4355df7e16a14baec4895525bfd11","tid":2223594,"uid":71213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"拜登畀刁大大騎撚住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c33380f340907ed42231dac963de328ed9412","tid":2223594,"uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"侵：拜登是習近平的走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48088bc92fb99687f5e34b0d80b4ab79da